ating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8467,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":254353,"username":"FaiChou","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/FaiChou","website":"https://faichou.com","twitter":"FaiChou_zh","psn":"","github":"FaiChou","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_mini.png?m=1684739460","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_normal.png?m=1684739460","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_large.png?m=1684739460","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1684739460","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1684739460","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7d0/b1a7/254353_xlarge.png?m=1684739460","created":1505371596,"last_modified":1684739460},"last_reply_by":"potatowish","last_touched":1688959431,"title":"你们喜欢 throw error 吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/955428","created":1688956242,"deleted":0,"content":"平时普通的业务逻辑开发中，越来越不想 throw error 了，而是返回空。\r\n\r\n比如 swift 中：\r\n\r\n```swift\r\nfunc req() async -> String? {\r\n  if let foo = try? await SomeAsyncThrowsFunc() {\r\n    return foo\r\n  }\r\n  return nil\r\n}\r\n\r\n用到的地方:\r\n\r\nTask {\r\n  if let val = await req() {\r\n    // get the string value\r\n  } else {\r\n    // somethings up\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n下面是使用 throw 的版本:\r\n\r\n```swift\r\nfunc req() async throws -> String {\r\n    if let foo = try await SomeAsyncThrowsFunc() {\r\n        return foo\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n用到的地方:\r\n\r\nTask {\r\n  do {\r\n      let val = try await req()\r\n      // get the string value\r\n  } catch {\r\n      // catch the error\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n或者直接将错误转换成 Optional 赋值:\r\nif let val = try? await req() {}\r\n```\r\n\r\n平时的业务逻辑没有写的那么完美，如果是写一个标准的库，定义所有的错误类型，遇到情况不对，throw 相对应的错误。但是到业务逻辑调用，函数包裹的越多，可能在中间一层将错误给抹掉，后面再也拿不到正确的错误值了。\r\n\r\n所以要想要规范，必须从头到尾规范起来，中间不能有松懈。但是，要偷懒，真的爽。（也承认自己写的不规范）","content_rendered":"<p>平时普通的业务逻辑开发中，越来越不想 throw error 了，而是返回空。</p>\n<p>比如 swift 中：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-swift\">func req() async -&gt; String? {\n  if let foo = try? await SomeAsyncThrowsFunc() {\n    return foo\n  }\n  return nil\n}\n\n用到的地方:\n\nTask {\n  if let val = await req() {\n    // get the string value\n  } else {\n    // somethings up\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>下面是使用 throw 的版本:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-swift\">func req() async throws -&gt; String {\n    if let foo = try await SomeAsyncThrowsFunc() {\n        return foo\n    }\n}\n\n用到的地方:\n\nTask {\n  do {\n      let val = try await req()\n      // get the string value\n  } catch {\n      // catch the error\n  }\n}\n\n或者直接将错误转换成 Optional 赋值:\nif let val = try? await req() {}\n</code></pre>\n<p>平时的业务逻辑没有写的那么完美，如果是写一个标准的库，定义所有的错误类型，遇到情况不对，throw 相对应的错误。但是到业务逻辑调用，函数包裹的越多，可能在中间一层将错误给抹掉，后面再也拿不到正确的错误值了。</p>\n<p>所以要想要规范，必须从头到尾规范起来，中间不能有松懈。但是，要偷懒，真的爽。（也承认自己写的不规范）</p>\n","last_modified":1688956242,"replies":10,"id":955428},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":206665,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3870,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":507506,"username":"aicfe","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/aicfe","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da3b/ee2d/507506_mini.png?m=1641457003","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da3b/ee2d/507506_normal.png?m=1641457003","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da3b/ee2d/507506_large.png?m=1641457003","created":1599724679,"last_modified":1641457003},"last_reply_by":"testver","last_touched":1688958430,"title":"想问下 V 友们在家里东西是如何进行收纳的","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/955426","created":1688955671,"deleted":0,"content":"有时候想找个啥东西总找不到，忘记了放在哪，用 app 来记录东西位置 是可行的吗","content_rendered":"<p>有时候想找个啥东西总找不到，忘记了放在哪，用 app 来记录东西位置 是可行的吗</p>\n","last_modified":1688955671,"replies":10,"id":955426},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785","name":"life","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785","title":"生活","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","topics":4581,"footer":"","header":"生活中的技术讨论","title_alternative":"Life","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","stars":1154,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":557,"parent_node_name":""},"member":{"id":500835,"username":"Fortississimo16","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Fortississimo16","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a361ed2d70ac2ab1990b38007db7c8af?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a361ed2d70ac2ab1990b38007db7c8af?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a361ed2d70ac2ab1990b38007db7c8af?s=73&d=retro","created":1595738274,"last_modified":1660141104},"last_reply_by":"BBrother","last_touched":1688959902,"title":"有没有人一起玩 OW2","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/955417","created":1688954942,"deleted":0,"content":"目前是双排，另一个姑娘希望能多一个女生一起玩，热闹一些。\r\n\r\n没有段位要求，我本人黄金白金水平，另一个是大师辅助。不需要太强，只是娱乐。\r\n\r\n我们两个都是话比较多的，不说脏话，不发脾气。一般是晚上下了班玩。\r\n\r\nplz","content_rendered":"<p>目前是双排，另一个姑娘希望能多一个女生一起玩，热闹一些。</p>\n<p>没有段位要求，我本人黄金白金水平，另一个是大师辅助。不需要太强，只是娱乐。</p>\n<p>我们两个都是话比较多的，不说脏话，不发脾气。一般是晚上下了班玩。</p>\n<p>plz</p>\n","last_modified":1688954942,"replies":10,"id":955417}]